        <p class="OnlineOnly">See <MadCap:xref href="../../../../Templates/D2H/About_Templates_and_Styles_D2H.htm">About Templates and Styles</MadCap:xref> and <MadCap:xref href="../../../../Introduction_Topics/D2H/Steps/Upgrading_Old_Projects.htm">Upgrading Old [%=Other.Product%] Projects</MadCap:xref>.</p>
